name: Men In Black : International
description: The Men in Black have always protected the Earth from the scum of the universe. In this new adventure, they tackle their biggest threat to date: a mole in the Men in Black organization.

name: Rocketman
description: The story of Elton John's life, from his years as a prodigy at the Royal Academy of Music through his influential and enduring musical partnership with Bernie Taupin.

name: Toy Story 4
description: Woody and Buzz embark on a quest to find Woody's romantic interest, Bo Peep.

name: Annabelle Comes Home
description: Determined to keep Annabelle from wreaking more havoc, demonologists Ed and Lorraine Warren bring the possessed doll to the locked artifacts room in their home, placing her safely behind sacred glass and enlisting a priest's holy blessing. But an unholy night of horror awaits as Annabelle awakens the evil spirits in the room, who all set their sights on a new target-the Warrens' ten-year-old daughter, Judy, and her friends.

name: Spider - Man : Far From Home
description: Following the events of Avengers: Endgame, Spider-Man must step up to take on new threats in a world that has changed forever.

name: Every Day A Good Day
description: Noriko is a university student. By her mother's recommendation, Noriko begins attending a Japanese tea ceremony near her house with her cousin Michiko. There, Noriko learns from Teacher Takeda. Noriko now has the Japanese tea ceremony in her life and it's there for her during moments when she is sad or happy.

name: Ma
description: In this new psychological horror-thriller from Tate Taylor and Blumhouse, a lonely woman befriends a group of teenagers and decides to let them party at her house. Just when the kids think their luck couldn't get any better, things start happening that make them question the intention of their host.

name: Anna
description: Beneath Anna Poliatova's striking beauty lies a secret that will unleash her indelible strength and skill to become one of the world's most feared government assassins.

name: Breaking Habits
description: A group of activists led by a self-proclaimed nun seek to legitimize their marijuana farm in Merced County, California.

name: Little Buddha
description: After the death of Lama Dorje, Tibetan Buddhist monks find three children - one American and two Nepalese - who may be the rebirth of their great teacher.

name: The Lion King
description: After the murder of his father, a young lion prince flees his kingdom only to learn the true meaning of responsibility and bravery.

name: The Current War
description: The dramatic story of the cutthroat race between electricity titans Thomas Edison and George Westinghouse to determine whose electrical system would power the modern world.

name: Child's Play
description: A mother gives her son a toy doll for his birthday, unaware of its more sinister nature.

name: A Dog's Journey
description: A dog finds the meaning of his own existence through the lives of the humans he meets.

name: Fast & Furious : Hobbs & Shaw
description: A spinoff of The Fate of the Furious, focusing on Johnson's US Diplomatic Security Agent Luke Hobbs forming an unlikely alliance with Statham's Deckard Shaw.

name: Scary Stories To Tell In The Dark
description: A group of teens face their fears in order to save their lives.

name: Detective Conan the Movie 23
description: The world's greatest blue sapphire, the blue lapis fist, said to have sunk in a pirate ship in the late 19th century, on the coasts of Singapore. A local millionaire plots to retrieve it, and when it's exhibited in an exhibition at the Singaporean Marina Sands hotel, a murder takes place.

name: Trouble
description: A pampered dog named Trouble must learn to live in the real world, while trying to escape from his former owner's greedy children.

name: The Art Of Racing In The Rain
description: A dog named Enzo recalls the life lessons he has learned from his race car driving owner, Denny.

name: Angel Has Fallen
description: Secret Service Agent Mike Banning is framed for the attempted assassination of the President and must evade his own agency and the FBI as he tries to uncover the real threat.
